Text: When you've got candids of her frenching her niece Emma, give us a call ...

When you've got any evidence of you with any sort of female creature whatsoever in person, while the creature is not dead, mutilated, or otherwise in an unconscious state, and you are holding a sign with the phrase "I am shadowyad on TPB, fuck off LTR" written on it, upload it on here.
